		'<center><img src="images/qwest/gadukino/new/Washfloor.jpg"></center>'
		'You are armed with a bucket and rag, and sat down on his haunches and began to scrub the floor. After everything was shining with cleanliness, you are satisfied put the inventory into a corner and went about their business.'

		act 'Go':gt'Gadhouse'
	end
elseif grandmahelping = 15:
